<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得赶到工地。”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得查出是什么引起陷坑出现的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西对着朋友们大声喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，朋友们！我很快就回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我……嗯……忘了带护膝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她飞快地从足球场跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不需要护膝！”特勒尔在她身后喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有足球训练！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，火箭女孩儿像闪电一样划过天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看！”玛拉说，“是火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞过美罗城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到到处都是大洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们看起来像是巨型鼹鼠洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到史密斯侦探在工地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正跟两个工人说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他旁边有一栋还没有完工的大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个工地到处都是大洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落在史密斯侦探身旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有什么事吗，侦探先生？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她笑着问，“您是在挖宝藏吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯皱着眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不好笑，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城里正在发生一些奇怪的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”罗西说，“到处都是大陷坑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人知道是什么引起的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“完全不知道。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们得马上查出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>东西掉进坑里不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有工地上的车辆都不见了，对吧？”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”一个工人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有的卡车，吊车和推土机都不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的车也不见了。”另一个工人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看上去很震惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它掉进地底下了！”她指着附近一个大洞说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你亲眼看到的吗？”史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个工人点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先是听到很大的轰鸣声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地面震动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>感觉像一场小地震，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后这个洞就出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的车刚好掉进去了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，轰隆！轰隆！地面剧烈地震动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”史密斯侦探叫道，“地震了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大楼晃动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一块大钢板掉下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心！”罗西叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探和工人们跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞起来接住了钢板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西把钢板安全地放在地上以后松了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探在吵闹的轰鸣中喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你认为是什么引起地震的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道！”罗西大声回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们得查出来……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西突然不说话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用超级听力听到一个新的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吵闹的轰鸣声中，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到意想不到的……说话的声音！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>